# Development Workflow Rules

## Building and Running
- Use Turbo for build orchestration: `yarn build` (runs `turbo build`)
- Dev server: `yarn dev` (runs `turbo dev`)
- Mobile: `yarn workspace expo-app start` or `yarn native`
- Web: `yarn workspace next-app dev` or `yarn web`

## Code Quality
- Always run TypeScript checks: `yarn type-check`
- Use Biome for linting and formatting
- Validate commits with lint-staged if configured

