# Common Commands
- `yarn install` - Install dependencies
- `yarn dev` - Start development servers (Turbo)
- `yarn build` - Build all packages (Turbo)
- `yarn type-check` - Run TypeScript checks
- `yarn workspace <name> add <package>` - Add package to specific workspace
- `yarn workspace <name> run <script>` - Run script in specific workspace
- `turbo build` - Direct Turbo build command
- `turbo dev` - Direct Turbo dev command
- `yarn workspaces list` - Shows all workspaces in your monorepo